OL,3,CHomes evacuated as large fire breaks
OL,4,Cout in Bracknell
OL,6,FThese dramatic pictures were captured
OL,7,Fby viewer Katie Redmond
OL,9,FA major fire has broken out in
OL,10,FBracknell.
OL,12,FPolice are evacuating people from
OL,13,Ftheir homes in the Peacock Lane area
OL,14,Ffollowing the blaze at the Daler
OL,15,FRowney headquarters.
OL,17,FSmoke can be seen for miles around.
OL,19,FThames Valley Police are using the
OL,20,Fnearby Waitrose car park as an RV
OL,21,Fpoint.
